text: The United States District Court for the District of South Carolina (in case citations, D.S.C.) is the federal district court. They cover the state of South Carolina. Court is held in the cities of Aiken, Anderson, Beaufort, Charleston, Columbia, Florence, Greenville, and Spartanburg. ==Other websites== * United States District Court for the District of South Carolina Official Website * United States Attorney for the District of South Carolina Official Website Category:Organizations based in South Carolina Category:Federal judiciary of the United States
title: United States District Court for the District of South Carolina
